import React from 'react' const WeatherItem = props => { const{ city, country, image, weather, date, time, temp, tempMax, tempMin, tempFeel, pressure, wind, clouds, humidity, sunrise, sunset, background, error} = props.weather let content = null if(!error && city){ content = (

{weather}

{date}

{time}

{city} {country}

{clouds}%

{humidity}%

{sunrise} {sunset}

{temp}°

odczuwalna {tempFeel}°

max:{tempMax}° min:{tempMin}°

{pressure} hPa

{wind}km/h

) } return (
{error ? `Brak danych dla podanego maista - ${city} nie istnieje lub zostało błędnie wpisane!` : content}
)} const weatherIcons = { 1:'/images/clouds.png', 2:'/images/sunrise.png', 3:'/images/sunset.png', 4:'/images/humidity.png', 5:'/images/temp.webp', 6:'/images/pressure.png', 7:'/images/wind.png', } export default WeatherItem
